
THE FLOW
--------

1. user pastes list of postcodes in a textbox, one per line

2. user pastes csv of postcodes with names in textbook

3. hits submit, which triggers a JS function

4. the mapbox API is called (in a parallel i/o way?) to convert postcodes to co-ordinates

- data structure of target venue:

  { postcode: "W1 1AZ",
    venue: true,
    name: "venue name",
    long: "0.00001",
    lat: "50.0001"
    }

- data structure of venues:

  [ venue1, venue2, venue3 ]